Journals Published

Throughout my academic and professional career, I have been dedicated to advancing the field of Ayurveda through rigorous research. My work has been recognized and published in several esteemed journals, including the Journal of Ayurveda and Integrative Medicine (JAIMS), the International Journal of Ayurvedic Research (IJAR), and the World Journal of Pharmaceutical Research (WJPR), among others. One of my proudest achievements is receiving the ISSN award for Best Researcher in Ayurveda, specifically for my original work on hydronephrosis.
